text: Do You Love Me is a 1946 American musical movie directed by Gregory Ratoff and starring Maureen O'Hara, Dick Haymes, Harry James, Reginald Gardiner, Richard Gaines. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. == Other websites == * * * * Category:1946 musical movies Category:American musical movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Gregory Ratoff
